    <h3>Homestay Programme in Shizuoka Prefecture</h3>
    <br>
    <img src="/images/japan/shizuoka04.jpg" alt="" class="img-responsive center-block">
    <br>
    <p>Homestay Programme in Shizuoka Prefecture started in 2001 between Shizuoka University and the Department of Japanese Studies (NUS) with the aim of providing NUS students with a better understanding of Japanese culture and lifestyle, as well as to improve their Japanese language proficiency.  Besides living with host families, the programme allows students to participate in various exchange sessions consisting of presentations and discussions with Shizuoka University students, and field trips within Shizuoka Prefecture.</p>
